  dct:description "Iscrizioni sepolcrali, spesso in forma di breve componimento in versi, che per lo più contengono le lodi del defunto"@it,
    "Funerary inscriptions, often in the form of short verse compositions, which typically contain praises of the deceased."@en;
  skos:inScheme <http://w3id.org/AMSHistorica/thesaurus>;
  skos:topConceptOf <http://w3id.org/AMSHistorica/thesaurus> .

